{
  "texts": [
    "In this role, AI could generate a diverse array of materials-ranging from essays and articles to case studies and data sets.",
    "These generated resources can then be presented to students for critical evaluation fostering a dynamic and interactive learning experience.",
    "This approach aligns with the observed strengths in students' critical evaluation skills, capitalising on an existing area of proficiency.",
    "By focusing on the critical evaluation of AI-generated content, educators can promote a more active form of learning.",
    "This requires students to delve deeply into the material, applying their analytical skills and making reasoned judgments."
  ]
}